PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F163A1776269466
OL,1,Wj5hw1~{4k7juhw1{$             G3/3
OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thu 30 Apr to Thu 14 May
OL,6,FSignals are not very strong for the
OL,7,Fextended forecast range, but in broad
OL,8,Fterms higher pressure is more likely
OL,9,Fto the north, with lower pressure to
OL,10,Fthe south. Across Scotland and
OL,11,Fnorthern half of England this would
OL,12,Fmean drier and more settled weather.
OL,13,FMeanwhile, Northern Ireland, Wales and
OL,14,Fthe southern half of England perhaps
OL,15,Fseeing a greater chance of rain or
OL,16,Fshowers at times, but plenty of scope
OL,17,Ffor fair weather in between.
OL,18,FTemperatures will probably be close to
OL,19,For slightly above average overall,
OL,20,Fperhaps becoming more widely warm at
OL,21,Ftimes.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
